    "body": "This is a security policy inside Chromium.  You would notice a similar thing occurring inside Chrome \n\nA file input can't be \"clicked\" on through JS unless it was triggered from a user interaction.  The workaround for this inside electron is to use the `userGesture` parameter of the `webContents.executeJavaScipt` method.\n\nhttps://github.com/electron/electron/blob/master/docs/api/web-contents.md#contentsexecutejavascriptcode-usergesture-callback\n"
